Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1306
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 12-10-17.1-12; IC 16-25-6; IC 16-27-2.
Synopsis: Prevention of elder abuse. Precludes certain individuals
who have been convicted of particular crimes from providing certain
types of in-home care for compensation. Prohibits the division of aging
from registering certain individuals for purposes of attendant care
services.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Lauer
January 6, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Public Health.
2026 IN 1306—LS 6903/DI 148

