3 the registration fee.
4 (6) Proof that the individual is at least eighteen (18) years of age.
5 (7) Any other information required by the division.
6 (b) A registration is valid for two (2) years. A personal services
7 attendant may renew the personal services attendant's registration by
8 updating any information in the file that has changed and by paying the
9 fee required under subsection (a)(5). The limited criminal history check
10 and report required under subsection (a)(2) and (a)(3) must be updated
